@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mchbmf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.27) - 0.99))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.15)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.68) * (tmp + 0.05 / tmp + 0.92)))
    tmp = ((tmp * 0.70) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.42) / (tmp + 0.81 / tmp + 0.93)))
    tmp = 0.53
    data[tid] = v0
